43
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:20,320
Zheng.

44
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,920
Don't let me down.

45
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:54,840
Anran is in danger.

46
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,640
Lieutenant Li, take him to He's mansion.

47
00:02:57,690 --> 00:02:58,560
Yes.

48
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,520
Someone.

49
00:03:00,660 --> 00:03:06,340
(Tianyi Pictures)

50
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,760
Candied haws.

51
