57
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,560
No.

58
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:08,880
Go ahead, you eat.

59
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:14,760
Is it good?

60
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:16,320
Delicious.

61
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,160
I'll buy it for you

62
