66
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,400
Okay.

67
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,920
♪Turning the last page♪

68
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,240
♪Only then did I realize♪

69
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:32,000
♪We have been apart for fifteen years♪

70
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,320
♪Through the rain of bullets♪

71
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,800
♪We barely survived♪

72
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:37,520
