78
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,440
♪They say it's out of reach♪

79
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,640
Every time I miss my mom,

80
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,280
I would take the tram.

81
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,080
She told me

82
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,480
(The Sincere Co. Ltd)
these are

83
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,260
the lights of the human world,

84
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,200
guiding the way to happiness.

85
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:07,720
From now on,

86
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,040
if you want to see it,

87
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:11,040
I'll accompany you.

88
00:06:14,970 --> 00:06:15,840
Deal.

89
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,120
You will always accompany me.

90
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:21,280
♪Words that should see the light♪

91
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:24,160
♪In the dead of night♪

92
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:26,800
♪Shaking my trembling fingers♪

93
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:29,640
♪Turning over the ashes in the basin♪

94
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:32,840
♪Crying silently in mourning♪

95
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:37,360
Don't worry.

96
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,300
I won't do anything to you.

97
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:48,200
My father is still in your hands.

98
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,000
I won't run away.

99
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,120
You don't need to follow me.

100
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,560
The world is not peaceful.

101
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,720
If you stir up any more issues,

102
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,760
it would harm my reputation.

103
00:07:08,280 --> 00:07:10,240
Are you worried about my purity?

104
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,120
That's not what I mean.

105
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:17,400
After you left, I opened a gallery.

106
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:20,920
I just wanted to sell a few paintings

107
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,320
to help my father a bit.

108
00:07:25,350 --> 00:07:27,000
Your father's case is indeed a myth.

109
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,480
Lieutenant Li is investigating it.

110
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,080
Don't interfere.

111
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,360
Better to rely on oneself.

112
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:32,880
Or maybe

113
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:35,240
