114
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,000
Not interested.

115
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:08,200
Sir, buy some flowers for the lady.

116
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,940
It's late, why aren't you home?

117
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,400
If I don't sell all the flowers,

118
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,280
Dad won't give me food.

119
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,320
I'll buy them all.

120
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:25,080
This silver dollar will
make your father praise you.

121
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,560
Thank you, sir.

122
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,000
But these flowers...

123
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,560
They don't cost this much.

124
00:08:33,920 --> 00:08:35,680
This one is for you.

125
00:08:36,160 --> 00:08:37,000
Hide it well.

126
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,400
Don't let your father find it.

127
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:40,040
Because your honesty

128
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,200
is more valuable than the money.

129
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:43,720
Go, go home.

130
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,840
Thank you.

131
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,040
Thank you.

132
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,240
First time to your place.

133
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,360
Can't go empty-handed, right?

134
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,840
Thank you.

135
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,600
You've already seen it.

136
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,480
We can leave now, right?

137
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,560
Just a reminder,

138
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:25,040
watching someone paint is very boring.

139
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:28,240
You probably
don't have the patience for it.

140
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,880
I'll return to your mansion myself.

141
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,480
No need for surveillance.

142
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:35,080
Can you paint a portrait for me?

143
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,560
I can paint a portrait for you.

144
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,360
But the condition is

145
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:48,520
I need to see my father.

146
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,200
Deal.

147
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,720
You look

148
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,760
very charming now.

149
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:27,160
But there's no warmth at all.

150
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,960
I only paint what I want,

151
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,440
including

152
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,200
the brother I can never find again.

153
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:45,400
I told you

154
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:47,800
not to bring up that word again.

155
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,320
I am Helian Zheng,

156
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:51,680
your husband,

157
00:11:52,160 --> 00:11:53,400
and the governor of Luan City.

158
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:55,240
I'm not your despised brother.

159
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,040
Helian Zheng.

160
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:27,840
Helian Zheng.

161
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,120
Helian Zheng.

162
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:35,920
Helian Zheng.

163
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:38,880
Why is it so hot?

164
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:41,680
Helian Zheng.

165
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:42,760
Wake up.

166
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,680
Helian Zheng.

167
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,280
You're injured.

168
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:54,920
Helian Zheng.

169
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:58,000
Helian Zheng.

170
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:02,360
Helian Zheng.

171
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:23,640
Madam, how is he doing?

172
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,560
Lieutenant Li.

173
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,000
The bleeding has stopped.

174
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,480
What about the test results?

175
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,200
This is a common snake venom.

176
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:30,960
The killer smeared it on the dagger.

177
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,600
But strangely,

178
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:34,840
if the killer intended to kill,

179
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:36,640
why not use a stronger poison?

180
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:39,120
These are afterthoughts.

181
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,320
Lieutenant Li.

182
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:43,440
When did the governor get poisoned?

183
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,440
This is critical.

184
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,640
About two hours ago.

185
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:48,760
On the tram,

186
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,760
an assassin was tailing you.

187
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,920
He got hurt while saving you.

188
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,840
He was injured saving me.

189
00:13:58,680 --> 00:14:00,040
But he didn't bring it up.

190
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:01,680
That's how he is.

191
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:04,400
Prefers to act more than explain.

192
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:06,040
Like with Mr. He's matter,

193
00:14:06,640 --> 00:14:08,160
