195
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:15,440
Lieutenant Li.

196
00:14:15,880 --> 00:14:16,760
Go find a doctor.

197
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,160
I'll stitch the wound first.

198
00:14:18,560 --> 00:14:20,920
Madam, you can stitch wounds?

199
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,680
My childhood friend studied medicine abroad.

200
00:14:23,680 --> 00:14:24,880
He taught me a bit.

201
00:14:25,750 --> 00:14:26,630
He said

202
00:14:26,630 --> 00:14:28,240
the antidote time for common snake venom

203
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,400
