204
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,600
- Hurry up.
- Yes.

205
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,040
Master.

206
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,320
It's all done.

207
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:52,360
We've found the largest drug dealer
in Luan City.

208
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:54,280
As long as he doesn't supply,

209
00:14:54,280 --> 00:14:55,400
they can't find the serum

210
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:56,880
to treat snake venom.

211
00:14:58,680 --> 00:14:59,520
Very good.

212
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:02,600
Master.

213
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:04,160
All 25 surgeons in Luan City

214
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:05,280
