215
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:06,480
No omissions.

216
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:09,080
Well done.

217
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,730
♪Blurry silhouette♪

218
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:31,040
(Brother,)

219
00:15:32,280 --> 00:15:34,440
(you must have endured a lot these years)

220
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:37,480
(to gain the position of Governor, right?)

221
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:41,200
(I've waited five years for you.)

222
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,120
(You mustn't die.)

223
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:47,800
(As long as you're safe,)

224
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,840
(I'll make prayer lamps with you)

225
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:53,840
(and only paint for you.)

226
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:58,120
♪Trapped in the sea of people♪

227
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:01,800
Brother, you're here.

228
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:04,080
I've noticed you've been

229
