236
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:24,280
Here you go.

237
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:26,680
This is what I made.

238
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:30,150
♪Join me in my dreams♪

239
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:31,120
You made this?

240
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:33,360
That's amazing!

241
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,330
Did you draw the pictures too?

242
00:16:35,340 --> 00:16:39,080
♪Have you seen the tomb's secret?♪

243
00:16:39,520 --> 00:16:40,600
Not as good as yours.

244
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:43,720
So beautiful.

245
00:16:46,040 --> 00:16:46,880
Thank you, brother.

246
00:16:47,920 --> 00:16:51,600
♪Blurry silhouette, dark soliloquy♪

247
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:54,520
♪Skipping tape♪

248
