♪Silent sentiments, shattered colors♪

249
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:02,600
♪All withered to dust♪

250
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:07,740
♪Shrouded in gloom, ideals are destroyed♪

251
00:17:13,810 --> 00:17:16,190
♪Like a drowning whale♪

252
00:17:17,410 --> 00:17:19,550
♪Falling into you♪

253
00:17:21,340 --> 00:17:23,630
♪Into every inch of your body♪

254
00:17:23,630 --> 00:17:26,740
♪Then it fell apart♪

255
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:29,120
♪Without a trace♪

256
00:17:29,120 --> 00:17:31,230
♪Like a warm winter♪

257
00:17:31,950 --> 00:17:33,900
♪Running barefoot to you♪

258
00:17:35,670 --> 00:17:38,860
♪Spreading in your cold palm♪

259
00:17:39,180 --> 00:17:41,740
♪Vanishing in your warm breath♪

